Getting historic league standing

Source: R/fct_historic_league_standing.R
get_league_historic_standings.Rd

This function returns a mini league's standings over time

get_league_historic_standings(league_number)

Arguments

league_number

the minileague number you want a table of

Examples

# Getting standings for my league across weeks
get_league_historic_standings(570437)
